{"tid":246192,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"公司有個肥婆同事成日有說話聽點應對?","createTime":"2017-05-16T20:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T16:34:36.000Z","uid":105552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bea36eb908788243bab0226f993c9f99601db968","tid":246192,"uid":105552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T20:48:13.000Z","msg":"細公司<br />\n開國元老黎 間公司開咁耐佢就係度咁耐<br />\n<br />\n轉左依份寫字樓新工都係三個月<br />\n間公司唔計老細得6條友 肥婆+2個老seafood+我地3個後生<br />\n日日都聽到佢同另1個老seafood講我地班後生既點點點<br />\n<br />\n唉 你話如果呀邊個邊個仲係度做就好喇 成件事暢順哂<br />\n我夾你夾埋呀xxx 大家都好有默契架<br />\n唔係話我想講依家d後生仔d咩 不過班90後真係唔捱得<br />\n總之就係個種指桑罵愧 有骨<br />\n<br />\n但係好神奇又會聽到佢成日係度講舊靚女同事壞話<br />\n講到自己好辛苦咁忍左佢兩年 又話點樣發佢脾四 佢做野點樣拿西<br />\n我唔知啦 我未係度做<br />\n<br />\n自問我地都無得罪佢 做個d野都係手板眼見功夫<br />\n佢為乜事要咁樣針對我地班後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地都心諗佢做乜9成日咁樣講野?<br />\n有個做左一排既就話佢係咁架 由佢啦<br />\n係咪肥婆通常都性格差架? <br />\n<br />\n我應該忍佢無視佢?自問我未夠成熟做唔到<br />\n定係交信走?<br />\n依家日日都要笑笑口同佢一齊做野真係好惡頂<br />\n<br />\n同埋點解細公司都可以搞到咁多是非?<br />\n一齊開開心心做哂野收工唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做飲食sale屎都無咁多是非 成班後生hehehaha又一day<br />\n<br />\n為左個肥婆而quit依份工<br />\n我覺得真係好唔抵<br />\n事關依份工唔chur唔hea 有野做到放工<br />\n呀頭嚴禁我地ot 夠鍾拍卡走得<br />\n同埋近屋企 <br />\n但係諗唔到點樣應對依件肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0cac87885256800ab69b02725c7a56a086758a","tid":246192,"uid":16270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T20:50:35.000Z","msg":"唔剪一條幾分鐘mv 俾你老細睇？"},{"pid":"ac2143b424df6c9315967d5568a453c509c237de","tid":246192,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T21:02:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e49b5bf911f621ccf8da9c4a3acf65fa8555c83","tid":246192,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T21:04:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0d2354dea2c70edda51eb983c104be17c94dbe5","tid":246192,"uid":13981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T21:04:56.000Z","msg":"咩話？又有肥婆？"},{"pid":"a95639992001a3eb1c2bc47b436b88a4d4b7714b","tid":246192,"uid":105552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:11:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔剪一條幾分鐘mv 俾你老細睇？</blockquote><br />\n老細其實都知架喇<br />\n不過做左咁耐野 點敢郁佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ddfab062341c8c4c3d9f305b6c1aee57bc226c6","tid":246192,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:45:14.000Z","msg":"好憎人講&quot;唔係話......不過&quot;<br />\n<br />\n屌就屌啦，屌屌下又縮咁即係點撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e404b0a00f30a909d35cff45c17f23440ac94f17","tid":246192,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:46:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩話？又有肥婆？</blockquote><br />\n肥婆咩年紀?"},{"pid":"2207dc448634a4b72281018fca9eee1847b0656b","tid":246192,"uid":105552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T04:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩話？又有肥婆？</blockquote><br />\n肥婆咩年紀?</blockquote><br />\n30到尾個D黎<br />\n唔老唔後生"},{"pid":"e6b1e5d4343586bf040264918d656a70f45e69cd","tid":246192,"uid":105552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d98d16477df025a57c98b1e449abe1e1c505639","tid":246192,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩話？又有肥婆？</blockquote><br />\n肥婆咩年紀?</blockquote><br />\n30到尾個D黎<br />\n唔老唔後生</blockquote><br />\n更年期<br />\n無人要<br />\n未破處<br />\n無青春<br />\n無錢<br />\n無身材<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心理變態"},{"pid":"03cf60c648810779febf87eb8bc8686c214648ba","tid":246192,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:30:16.000Z","msg":"我-&gt;即走"},{"pid":"57a8f0c7d551ceb05305fb243b91ea821433326e","tid":2